title: 3rd Brother - Graphic Novel
creator: Travis Rogers
description: After uncovering an ancient knowledge, a man named Avid becomes obsessed with discovering the mysteries of time. This ancient knowledge speaks of a way to gain immortality by entering a void between the moments of time. Avid begins to experiment on the surrounding Townspeople and his own brothers.
